WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.866
Why did grandpa suddenly make a will?

2
00:00:02.066 --> 00:00:03.500
My aunt is back from America

3
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:06.166
I have been with the old man these days

4
00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.366
It must have been his idea to make another will

5
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:10.666
Why did he come back suddenly?

6
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:12.000
He already knows you're crippled

7
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.366
Dongfang Run's return this time is obviously for you

8
00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:18.066
So brother, you must be mentally prepared

9
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:19.366
Embrace a fierce battle

10
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:20.766
Nothing to prepare for.

11
00:00:20.966 --> 00:00:23.066
Anyway, he didn't like me growing up

12
00:00:23.266 --> 00:00:24.166
used to it

13
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:39.066
Doctor, how is my grandfather's illness?

14
00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:40.933
Your deposit is very serious.

15
00:00:40.933 --> 00:00:42.000
Anyway.

16
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:43.566
Please save my grandfather

17
00:00:43.566 --> 00:00:44.966
We will make a password.

18
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:49.666
You have been biased towards my brother since you were a child

19
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:51.400
My brother is not there, and you prefer to ride Xuanxuan

20
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:52.366
I kind of figured it out.

21
00:00:52.366 --> 00:00:53.666
You are patriarchal.

22
00:00:53.666 --> 00:00:55.666
Treat me and Runer as outsiders

23
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:57.166
In my heart

24
00:00:57.166 --> 00:00:59.166
You're all the same.

25
00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.266
Then Xuanxuan returned to your will

26
00:01:01.266 --> 00:01:02.500
Married a wife like that

27
00:01:02.566 --> 00:01:04.166
Now you treat Rui Ao so much

28
00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:05.966
You still don't want to cut the will

29
00:01:05.966 --> 00:01:07.700
And give him the oil ornament

30
00:01:07.766 --> 00:01:09.866
How can we be the same in your heart?

31
00:01:09.866 --> 00:01:13.066
I want to wait for him to come and ask in person

32
00:01:14.666 --> 00:01:15.466
Ah!

33
00:01:17.866 --> 00:01:21.000
Grandpa, you are also a concubine who protects your wife

34
00:01:21.166 --> 00:01:22.700
But the wife you're looking for

35
00:01:22.700 --> 00:01:25.933
It's really not suitable for us to be the mistress of the house

36
00:01:25.933 --> 00:01:30.800
Grandpa wants you to divorce him immediately

